FAQÔÉÅ

Q: Where are the trained models? A: In the top-level models/ folder (models/xgboost_model.joblib).

Q: How do I view MLflow runs? A: Run mlflow ui and open the URL it displays.

Q: How can I speed up hyperparameter tuning? A: Reduce n_trials in the Optuna study or sample the dataset.

Q: Where are monitoring reports saved? A: Check src/*/reports/ for JSON monitoring output.
